00:32:13,120 --> 00:32:14,320
is a little...

547
00:32:17,360 --> 00:32:18,400
A little...

548
00:32:18,840 --> 00:32:19,960
What are you trying to say?

549
00:32:20,640 --> 00:32:23,760
